EARN EXTRA MONEY!BE YOUR OWN BOSS!We are seeking a person ad date: 10/07/2015 
EARN EXTRA MONEY!BE YOUR OWN BOSS!We are seeking a person to deliver newspapers to homes in Brookings.Route is approximately 2-3 hours a day, only 2 times per week, early mornings. This is an independent contracted delivery route. You must be over 18 with a valid drivers license, proof of insurance and reliable vehicles.Must have ability to work with little supervision and provide prompt, efficient service.This is an excellent opportunity for extra cash to supplement any income.Receive $100 Sign-on Bonus!INTERESTED?For details contact:The Circulation Department djeffcoat@currypilot.com 541-469-3123 Click image to enlarge
